.TH MPRIS-MINIPLAYER 1 "June 2026" "MPRIS MiniPlayer 1.2.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
mpris-miniplayer \- control MPRIS-compatible media players
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B mpris-miniplayer
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B MPRIS MiniPlayer
is a compact GTK4/libadwaita controller for Linux media players that expose the
MPRIS interface on the session D-Bus.
.PP
It shows track metadata and playback controls for the selected player.
.SH OPTIONS
This program does not currently define command-line options.
.SH AUTHOR
Christian Lauinger
